en_question:
    To ensure the normal operation of a certain piece of equipment, it is necessary to determine the number of spare parts for three different components $A_1$, $A_2$, and $A_3$, which work in series. Increasing the number of spare parts can improve the equipment’s operational reliability but also increases the cost. The total investment is limited to 8 thousand yuan.The relationship between the number of spare parts, their reliability, and their cost is shown in Table 7-19. Determine how many spare parts should be allocated for each of $A_1$, $A_2$, and $A_3$ to maximize the equipment’s operational reliability (i.e., maximize the sum of the logarithms of the component reliabilities).
Formulate and solve the mathematical model.
\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{Relationship between number of spare parts, reliability, and cost (Table 7-19)}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|ccc|ccc}
        \toprule
        Number of Spares & \multicolumn{3}{c|}{Reliability} & \multicolumn{3}{c}{Cost of Spare Parts （thousand yuan）} \\
        \cmidrule(lr){2-4} \cmidrule(lr){5-7}
        & $A_1$ & $A_2$ & $A_3$ & $A_1$ & $A_2$ & $A_3$ \\
        \midrule
        1 & 0.3 & 0.2 & 0.1 & 1 & 3 & 2 \\
        2 & 0.4 & 0.5 & 0.2 & 2 & 5 & 3 \\
        3 & 0.5 & 0.9 & 0.7 & 3 & 6 & 4 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

cn_question:
    为保证某设备正常运转，需对串联工作的三种不同零件 $A_1, A_2, A_3$ 分别确定备件数量。若增加备用零件的数量，可提高设备正常运转的可靠性，但费用要增加，而总投资额为 8 千元。已知备用零件数量与它的可靠性和费用关系如表 7-19 所示，求 $A_1, A_2, A_3$ 的备用零件数量各为多少时，可使设备运转的可靠性最高（最大化设备总可靠性的对数和）。
使用数学模型求解
\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{备用零件数量与可靠性及费用关系（表 7-19）}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|ccc|ccc}
        \toprule
        备件数 & \multicolumn{3}{c|}{可靠性} & \multicolumn{3}{c}{备用零件费用 / 千元} \\
        \cmidrule(lr){2-4} \cmidrule(lr){5-7}
        & $A_1$ & $A_2$ & $A_3$ & $A_1$ & $A_2$ & $A_3$ \\
        \midrule
        1 & 0.3 & 0.2 & 0.1 & 1 & 3 & 2 \\
        2 & 0.4 & 0.5 & 0.2 & 2 & 5 & 3 \\
        3 & 0.5 & 0.9 & 0.7 & 3 & 6 & 4 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}
